's%20Address%20Adds%20Fire%20To%20BJP's%20Emergency%20Offensive%20Against%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Emergency%20imposed%20in%201975%20was%20the%20darkest%20chapter%20of%20a%20direct%20attack%20on%20the%20Constitution%2C%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20said%20today%20in%20her%20address%20to%20a%20joint%20sitting%20of%20Parliament.%20This%20is%20her%20first%20address%20to%20Parliament%20after%20the%20general%20election%20elected%20a%20new%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution%2C%20she%20said%2C%20has%20stood%20up%20to%20every%20challenge%20and%20every%20test%20in%20the%20past%20decades.%20%26quot%3BToday%20is%2027th%20June.%20The%20imposition%20of%20Emergency%20on%2025th%20June%2C%201975%2C%20was%20the%20biggest%20and%20darkest%20chapter%20of%20direct%20attack%20on%20the%20Constitution.%20The%20entire%20country%20felt%20outraged.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20country%20emerged%20victorious%20over%20such%20unconstitutional%20forces%20as%20the%20traditions%20of%20the%20republic%20lie%20at%20the%20core%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20amid%20cheers%20from%20the%20treasury%20benches%20and%20protests%20by%20the%20Opposition.%C2%A0Vice-President%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20echoed%20the%20President%20on%20the%20Emergency%20and%20said%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Battacked%20the%20Constitution%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President's%20remark%20comes%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20heated%20exchange%20between%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20the%20Opposition%20on%20Emergency.%20While%20central%20ministers%2C%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20have%20stressed%20on%20the%20horrors%20of%20the%20Emergency%20imposed%20by%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20have%20said%20an%20%26quot%3Bundeclared%20emergency%26quot%3B%20is%20in%20the%20force%20over%20the%20past%2010%20years%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President's%20remarks%20also%20play%20out%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20Opposition's%20Constitution%20push.%20In%20demonstrations%20outside%20the%20House%20and%20proceedings%20inside%20it%2C%20Opposition%20MPs%20have%20been%20holding%20up%20copies%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20accusing%20the%20ruling%20party%20of%20undermining%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20Government%20also%20does%20not%20consider%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20as%20just%20a%20medium%20of%20governance%3B%20rather%20we%20are%20making%20efforts%20to%20ensure%20that%20our%20Constitution%20becomes%20a%20part%20of%20public%20consciousness%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20President%20said%20in%20her%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President's%20address%20to%20Parliament%20is%20broadly%20a%20document%20that%20outlines%20the%20government's%20achievements%20and%20lays%20out%20is%20vision%20for%20the%20future.%20The%20address%20is%20essentially%20prepared%20by%20the%20government%20and%20is%20followed%20by%20a%20debate%20on%20the%20Motion%20of%20Thanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20the%20President%20said%2C%20has%20become%20the%20fastest%20growing%20major%20economy%20in%20the%20world%20and%20has%20gone%20from%20the%2011th%20spot%20in%202014%20to%20the%205th%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20size%20of%20economy.%20She%20said%20the%20government%20is%20now%20focused%20on%20its%20goal%20of%20making%20India%20the%20third-largest%20economy.%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20is%20giving%20equal%20priority%20to%20all%20three%20arms%3A%20manufacturing%2C%20services%20and%20agriculture.%20India%20is%20becoming%20Atmanirbhar%20in%20every%20field%20at%20a%20rapid%20pace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President's%20address%20also%20touched%20upon%20the%20burning%20issue%20surrounding%20irregularities%20in%20the%20National%20Eligibility%20cum%20Entrance%20Test%20(NEET)%2C%20an%20all-India%20exam%20for%20admission%20to%20medical%20courses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20she%20said%2C%20is%20fully%20committed%20to%20investigating%20the%20recent%20incidents%20of%20paper%20leaks%20and%20ensure%20that%20the%20guilty%20are%20punished.%20As%20she%20made%20the%20remarks%2C%20cries%20of%20%26quot%3BNEET%26quot%3B%20were%20heard%20from%20the%20Opposition%20benches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSanctity%2C%20transparency%20are%20a%20must%20in%20government%20recruitments%20and%20examinations.%20The%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20conduct%20fair%20investigation%20and%20ensure%20the%20most%20stringent%20punishment%20to%20those%20guilty%20in%20the%20recent%20incidents%20of%20paper%20leak%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20rise%20above%20%26quot%3Bpartisan%20politics%26quot%3B%20and%20take%20strong%20steps%20on%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20on%20the%20need%20for%20the%20Parliament%20to%20run%20smoothly%2C%20she%20said%20opposition%20of%20policies%20and%20obstruction%20of%20parliamentary%20functioning%20are%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Parliament%20conducts%20its%20business%20smoothly%2C%20when%20healthy%20deliberations%20take%20place%20here%2C%20when%20far-reaching%20decisions%20are%20taken%2C%20then%20the%20people%20repose%20confidence%20not%20only%20in%20the%20Government%20but%20also%20in%20the%20entire%20system.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20every%20moment%20of%20Parliament%20will%20be%20fully%20utilised%20and%20public%20interest%20will%20be%20given%20priority%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719474240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fcmi08p8g_droupadi-murmu_625x300_27_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Femergency-was-biggest-attack-on-constitution-president-murmu-5980028%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Emergency%20imposed%20in%201975%20was%20the%20biggest%20attack%20and%20a%20blot%20on%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20said%20today%20in%20her%20address%20t