990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELIVE%3A%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20addresses%20both%20Houses%20of%20the%20Parliament%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F4hNviAsCmv%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F4hNviAsCmv%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20President%20of%20India%20(%40rashtrapatibhvn)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frashtrapatibhvn%2Fstatus%2F1806199471975567588%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2027%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20all%20remember%20those%20times%20when%20ballot%20papers%20were%20snatched%20and%20looted%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Murmu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Kashmir%20Polls%20Befitting%20Reply%20To%20Enemies%20of%20India'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffull-text-of-president-droupadi-murmus-parliament-address-historic-steps-will-be-seen-in-budget-5980217%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Droupadi%20Murmu%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20congratulated%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20for%20the%20high%20voter%20turnout%20recorded%20in%20the%20union%20territory%20in%20the%20recent%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20very%20heartening%20aspect%20of%20this%20election%20emerged%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20The%20Kashmir%20Valley%20broke%20all%20records%20of%20voter%20turnout%20of%20many%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20four%20decades%2C%20we%20had%20witnessed%20low%20voter%20turnout%20amidst%20shutdowns%20and%20strikes%20in%20Kashmir.%20Enemies%20of%20India%20continued%20to%20spread%20false%20propaganda%20at%20global%20forums%2C%20projecting%20it%20as%20an%20opinion%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20But%20this%20time%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%20has%20given%20a%20befitting%20reply%20to%20every%20such%20element%20within%20the%20country%20and%20outside%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-with-over-58-per-cent-polling-jammu-and-kashmir-records-highest-voter-turnout-in-35-years-5756260%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20recorded%20the%20highest%20voter%20turnout%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20in%20last%2035%20years.%20The%20combined%20voter%20turnout%20at%20the%20polling%20stations%20for%20the%20entire%20Union%20Territory%20with%20five%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20was%2058.46%20per%20cent%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20express%20my%20gratitude%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20on%20behalf%20of%20crores%20of%20Indians%20today.%20This%20was%20the%20largest%20election%20in%20the%20world.%20About%2064%20crore%20voters%20performed%20their%20duty%20with%20enthusiasm%20and%20zeal%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Murmu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Whole%20World%20Talking%20About%20Lok%20Sabha%20Elections%202024'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20address%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstrictest-punishment-for-neet-accused-president-murmu-in-parliament-5980002%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Murmu%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20said%20that%20the%C2%A0whole%20world%20is%20talking%20about%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Elections%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20is%20witnessing%20that%20the%20people%20of%20India%20have%20elected%20a%20stable%20Government%20with%20a%20clear%20majority%2C%20consecutively%20for%20the%20third%20term%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20alliance%2C%20NDA%2C%20winning%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20happened%20after%20six%20decades%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%20took%20oath%20as%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20a%20record%20third%20term%2C%20equalling%20first%20Prime%20Minister%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru's%20record%20of%20three%20wins.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20of%20India%20have%20full%20faith%20that%20only%20my%20Government%20can%20fulfill%20their%20aspirations.%20Therefore%2C%20this%20election%20of%202024%20has%20been%20an%20election%20of%20trust%20in%20policy%2C%20intention%2C%20dedication%2C%20and%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Murmu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719473880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fdgvmvum_president-droupadi-murmu_625x300_27_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-passed-every-test-president-droupadi-murmu-praises-evms-in-parliament-address-to-new-lok-sabha-rajya-sabha-mps-5980319%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20concerns%20raised%20over%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20by%20several%20opposition%20parties%2C%20President%20Draupadi%20Murmu%20today%20praised%20the%20EVMs%20in%20her%20address%20to%20the%20joint%20session%20of%20the%20Parliament.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-passed-every-test-president-droupadi-murmu-praises-evms-in-parliament-address-to-new-lok-sabha-rajya-sabha-mps-5980319%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-passed-every-test-president-droupadi-murmu-praises-evms-in-parliament-address-to-new-lok-sabha-rajya-sabha-mps-5980319%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-passed-every-test-president-droupadi-murmu-praises-evms-in-parliament-address-to-new-lok-sabha-rajya-sabha-mps-5980319%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ratan%