-murmu-to-address-joint-sitting-of-parliament-today-5979418%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAddressing%20a%20joint%20sitting%20of%20both%20Houses%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20the%20first%20in%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20third%20term%2C%20and%20one%20likely%20to%20be%20rocked%20by%20opposition%20protests%20over%20the%20NEET%20row%20-%20Ms%20Murmu%20said%20the%20government%20is%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%20to%20a%20fair%20investigation%26quot%3B%20and%20vowed%20%26quot%3Bstrict%20punishment%20to%20the%20culprits%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20recent%20irregularities%20and%20paper%20leaks%20are%20being%20dealt%20with%20strongly%20(and)%20the%20government's%20focus%20is%20on%20improving%20the%20exam%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20President%20said%20amid%20an%20uproar%20over%20the%20word%20'NEET'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20incidents%20(leaked%20question%20papers)%20have%20happened%20in%20many%20states...%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20measures%20beyond%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20assembled%20MPs%20from%20the%20ruling%20and%20opposition%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcerns%20over%20the%20NEET%20exam%20were%20flagged%20after%20an%20unusually%20high%20number%20of%20students%20-%20a%20record%2067%2C%20including%20six%20from%20one%20coaching%20centre%20-%20scored%20a%20perfect%20720%20in%20an%20uber-competitive%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20also%20red%20flags%20over%20'grace%20marks'%20to%201%2C563%20students.%20On%20paper%20these%20were%20for%20students%20who%20ran%20out%20of%20time%2C%20but%20it%20was%20later%20confirmed%20there%20is%20no%20protocol%20for%20award%20of%20such%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20was%20tasked%20with%20investigating%20allegations%20of%20leaked%20question%20papers%20and%20criminal%20gangs%2C%20dubbed%20'solver%20gangs'.%20Multiple%20arrests%20-%20from%20Bihar%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Maharashtra%20have%20been%20made%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20four%20men%20arrested%20from%20Bihar%20was%20Anurag%20Yadav%2C%20a%20NEET%20aspirant%20who%20confessed%20that%20he%2C%20and%20his%20friends%2C%20had%20received%20copies%20of%20the%20question%20paper%2024%20hours%20before%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-paper-was-leaked-4-arrested-students-tell-bihar-police-5928622%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BGot%20NEET%20Paper%20Night%20Before%20Exam%26quot%3B%3A%20Arrested%20Student%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYadav%20-%20who%20was%20prepping%20at%20coaching%20centre%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Kota%20-%20told%20cops%20he%20had%20been%20summoned%20home%20by%20his%20uncle%2C%20Sikandar%20P%20Yadavendu%2C%20a%20municipal%20employee%20who%20purchased%20copies%20of%20the%20question%20paper%20from%20two%20other%20accused%2C%20and%20sold%20them%20for%20a%20profit%20to%20Yadav's%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20arrested%20include%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-who-is-sanjeev-mukhiya-the-alleged-mastermind-behind-neet-paper-leak-5963858%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESaneev%20Mukhiya%20from%20Bihar%2C%20whom%20cops%20have%20called%20%26quot%3Bthe%20mastermind%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Iranna%20Kongalwar%20from%20Maharashtra%2C%20who%20ran%20a%20coaching%20centre%20in%20the%20city%20of%20Latur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-paper-leak-case-maharashtra-accused-iranna-kongalwar-half-shut-windows-abandoned-scooters-at-neet-paper-leak-accuseds-home-5973405%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHalf-Shut%20Windows%2C%20Scooters%20At%20NEET%20Leak%20Accused's%20Home%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20CBI%20team%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcbi-team-questions-jharkhand-school-principal-in-neet-paper-leak-case-5975764%5C%22%20target%3D%5C