adgets%2Flenovo-legion-go-handheld-gaming-console-launched-in-india-at-rs-89-990-124062700407_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BShould%20Be%20Fair%20Contest%26quot%3B%3A%20Afghanistan%20Coach%20Fumes%20At%20ICC%20After%20T20%20WC%20Exit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfghanistan's%20heroic%20run%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20came%20to%20an%20end%20at%20the%20penultimate%20hurdle%2C%20as%20the%20Rashid%20Khan-led%20side%20suffered%20a%20lopsided%209-wicket%20defeat%20against%20South%20Africa%20in%20Trinidad.%20Opting%20to%20bat%20first%2C%20Afghanistan%20could%20only%20put%2056%20runs%20on%20the%20board%2C%20their%20lowest%20in%20T20%20internationals%20and%20also%20the%20lowest%20in%20the%20history%20of%20T20%20World%20Cups.%20After%20Afghanistan's%20journey%20in%20the%20competition%20came%20to%20an%20end%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20head%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jonathan%20Trott%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F928-jonathan-trott-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJonathan%20Trott%3C%2Fa%3E%20fumed%20at%20ICC%2C%20saying%20it%20wasn't%20even%20an%20%26quot%3Beven%20contest%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20media%20at%20the%20press%20conference%20after%20game%2C%20Trott%20said%20that%20though%20he%20doesn't%20want%20to%20get%20himself%20into%20any%20trouble%2C%20he%20does%20want%20to%20highlight%20the%20poor%20nature%20of%20the%20pitch%20that%20was%20prepared%20for%20a%20clash%20as%20big%20as%20a%20World%20Cup%20semi-final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20get%20myself%20into%20trouble.%20But%20I%20also%20don't%20want%20to%20sound%20a%20bit%20like%20'sour%20grapes'%20but%20that's%20not%20the%20pitch%20that%20you%20want%20to%20have%20a%20semi-final%20of%20a%20World%20Cup%20on.%20Plain%20and%20simple.%20It%20should%20be%20a%20fair%20contest.%20I'm%20not%20saying%20it%20should%20be%20completely%20flat%20with%20no%20spin%20and%20seam%20movement%2C%20you%20shouldn't%20have%20batters%20worrying%20about%20moving%20forward%20and%20having%20the%20ball%20fly%20over%20their%20head.%20You%20should%20be%20confident%20in%20getting%20through%20the%20line%20or%20use%20their%20skills.%20And%20T20%20is%20all%20about%20attacking%20and%20scoring%20runs%20and%20taking%20wickets.%20Not%20looking%20to%20survive%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Trott%20during%20the%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrott%20wanted%20the%20pitch%20to%20offer%20something%20to%20both%20his%20side%20and%20South%20Africa.%20However%2C%20he%20feels%20his%20team%20was%20undone%20by%20a%20surface%20that%20favoured%20the%20opponent%20team%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20opposition%20bowled%20well%20and%20gets%20you%20into%20a%20position%20after%20bowling%20well%20and%20through%20skill%2C%20then%20it's%20fine%20to%20them.%20Then%20it's%20about%20adapting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20had%20bowled%20the%20way%20South%20Africa%20had%2C%20you%20could%20have%20seen%20a%20different%20second%20half%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20during%20the%20chat%20with%20media%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJonathan%20Trott%20on%20Afghanistan's%20Schedule%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrott%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20hectic%20schedule%20that%20the%20Afghanistan%20team%20was%20exposed%20to.%20But%2C%20he%20didn't%20point%20finger%20at%20the%20schedule%20as%20the%20reason%20behind%20his%20team's%20embarrassing%20defeat%20in%20the%20semi-final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20only%20got%20back%20to%20hotel%20at%20three%20o'clock%20and%20then%20we%20had%20to%20leave%20at%20eight%20o'clock%20--%20five%20hours%20later%20so%20we%20didn't%20get%20much%20sleep%20so%20the%20guys%20obviously%20were%20very%20tired%20and%20a%20lot%20to%20process%20really%20emotionally%20physically.%20So%20all%20new%20territory%20for%20the%20guys%2C%26quot%3B%20Trott%20said%20Having%20said%20that%2C%20Trott%20conceded%20they%20were%20outplayed%20by%20a%20strong%20South%20African%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20we%20knew%20the%20schedule%2C%20so%20that's%20not%20an%20excuse%20as%20such.%20When%20you%20go%20in%20World%20Cups%20or%20tournaments%2C%20you%20can't%20have%20everything%20your%20own%20way%2C%20and%20you've%20got%20to%20fight%20and%20play%20against%20the%20odds%20which%20you've%20done%20at%20times%20and%20very%20proud%20of%20that.%20But%20it's%20no%2C%20it's%20not%20the%20reason%20why%20we%20didn't%20win%20today.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BSouth%20Africa%20bowled%20well%2C%20used%20the%20conditions%2C%20and%20showed%20our%20boys%20what%20it's%20capable%20of.%20But%20it%20just%20didn't%20go%20our%20way%20tonight.%26quot%3B%20The%2043-year-old%20hoped%20that%20the%20semifinal%20loss%20serves%20as%20a%20learning%20for%20the%20team%20that%20has%20improved%20leaps%20and%20bounds%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...we've%20obviously%20got%20one%20better%20than%20the%20previous%20(ODI)%20World%20Cup%20in%20November%20and%20it's%20just%20about%20taking%20it%20step%20by%20step%20and%20hopefully%20we%20learn%20from%20today%2C%20the%20batters%20certainly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20it%20takes%20to%20play%20international%20cricket%20and%20play%20against%20a%20bowling%20side%20like%20South%20Africa%20on%20a%20pitch%20that's%20perhaps%20not%20conducive%20to%20high%20scoring%20runs%20and%20finding%20ways%20of%20winning%20games...we%20just%20couldn't%20find%20a%20way%20today.%26quot%3B%20Openers%20Rahmanullah%20Gurbaz%20(0)%20and%20Ibrahim%20Zadran%20(2)%2C%20who%20were%20Afghanistan's%20top%20run-getters%20in%20the%20tournament%2C%20both%20failed%2C%20putting%20pressure%20on%20the%20middle%20order%20that%20hadn't%20fired%20at%20all%20in%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20else%20has%20got%20runs.%20We%20need%20to%20find%20a%20reason%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Trott%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20defeat%20to%20South%20Africa%2C%20Afghanistan%20can%20keep%20their%20heads%20high%2C%20having%20made%20a%20mark%20in%20the%20tournament%20and%20elevating%20their%20status%20as%20an%20elite%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719473160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F66vfpu0g_trott-and-rashid-x_625x300_27_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fshould-be-a-fair-contest-afghanistan-coach-fumes-at-icc-after-t20-world-cup-semi-final-defeat-5979979%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Afghanistan%20head%20coach%20Jonathan%20Trott%20didn't%20hold%20it%20back%20after%20his%20team's%20semi-final%20defeat%20against%20South%20Africa%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fshould-be-a-fair-contest-afghanistan-coach-fumes-at-icc-after-t20-world-cup-semi-final-defeat-5979979%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fshould-be-a-fair-contest-afghanistan-coach-fumes-at-icc-after-t20-world-cup-semi-final-defeat-5979979%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fshould-be-a-fair-contest-afghanistan-coach-fumes-at-icc-after-t20-world-cup-semi-final-defeat-5979979%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prabhas%20takes%20a%20pay%20cut%20for%20Kalki%202898%20AD%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719473136000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111307179%2Cimgsize-979394.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fprabhas-take-a-pay-cut-for-kalki-2898-ad-deepika-padukone-amitabh-bachchan-charged-rs-20-crore-report%2Farticleshow%2F111307319.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111307319.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPrabh