d%20the%20overall%20rankings%20and%20fairness%20of%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20has%20also%20been%20tasked%20with%20probing%20several%20cases%20related%20to%20the%20alleged%20paper%20leak%20and%20exam%20rigging.%20The%20CBI's%20investigation%20spans%20multiple%20states%20and%20has%20already%20led%20to%20the%20questioning%20of%20individuals%20and%20several%20arrests%20connected%20to%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%2C%20represented%20by%20the%20coaching%20centre%20and%20other%20students%2C%20argued%20for%20students'%20right%20to%20access%20their%20Optical%20Mark%20Recognition%20(OMR)%20sheets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Justice%20Manoj%20Mishra%20and%20Justice%20SVN%20Bhatti%2C%20presiding%20over%20the%20case%2C%20questioned%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20allegedly%20violated%20by%20the%20NTA's%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20joint%20sitting%20of%20Parliament%20earlier%20today%2C%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20said%20that%20the%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20probing%20the%20allegations%20concerning%20exam%20paper%20leaks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20due%20to%20any%20reason%2C%20there%20is%20an%20obstruction%20in%20examinations%20it%20is%20not%20appropriate.%20Sanctity%20and%20transparency%20are%20a%20must%20in%20government%20recruitments%20and%20examinations%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20conducting%20a%20fair%20investigation%20and%20ensuring%20the%20most%20stringent%20punishment%20to%20those%20guilty%20in%20the%20recent%20incidents%20of%20paper%20leak.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719473040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fm6tes5mg_neet-protest_625x300_24_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-issues-notice-to-exam-body-nta-over-alleged-inconsisten