hat%20he%20saw%20holes%20drilled%20improperly%2C%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20%26quot%3Bcatastrophe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20airplane%20mechanic%20said%20he%20was%20fired%20from%20his%20job%20shortly%20after%20raising%20concerns.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20Boeing%20whistleblower%20has%20come%20forward%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20witnessed%20787%20Dreamliner%20planes%20being%20built%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bcatastrophe%20down%20the%20line.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichard%20Cuevas%20was%20a%20Strom%20airplane%20mechanic%20who%20used%20to%20work%20as%20a%20contractor%20for%20Boeing%20and%20Spirit%20AeroSystems.%20He%20said%20that%20in%202023%2C%20he%20witnessed%20substandard%20manufacturing%20of%20the%20787%20planes'%20forward%20pressure%20bulkheads%2C%20which%20help%20maintain%20air%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkatzbanks.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F240625-Ltr-to-Whitaker.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomplaint%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20by%20his%20lawyers%20on%20Tuesday%20to%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%2C%20Cuevas%20said%20Spirit%20AeroSystems%20workers%20were%20drilling%20holes%20into%20the%20fasteners%20of%20the%20plane's%20forward%20pressure%20bulkhead%2C%20which%20were%20bigger%20than%20what%20Boeing%20had%20specified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20did%20this%20to%20%26quot%3Bclear%20excess%20paint%20from%20the%20holes%20and%20speed%20up%20a%20slow%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20complaint.%20Cuevas%20said%20that%20the%20faults%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20loss%20of%20air%20pressure%20in%20the%20flight%20and%20run%20the%20risk%20of%20power%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20March%2C%20a%20few%20months%20after%20he%20reported%20his%20findings%20to%20Boeing%20and%20Spirit%20AeroSystems%2C%20he%20was%20fired%20from%20his%20job%2C%20the%20complaint%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%2C%20Boeing%20said%20it%20had%20inves