men%20and%20its%20safety%20protocol%2C%20which%20requires%20all%20employees%20to%20avoid%20wearing%20metal%20irrespective%20of%20gender%20or%20religion%2C%20is%20not%20discriminatory%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20informal%20note%20shared%20with%20the%20government%20after%20reports%20suggested%20it%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffoxconn-doesnt-hire-married-women-at-chennai-plant-centre-seeks-report-5976087%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bnot%20hiring%20married%20women%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Foxconn%20stated%20that%20such%20stipulations%20are%20not%20part%20of%20its%20policy%20and%20these%20claims%20may%20have%20been%20made%20by%20those%20individuals%20who%20were%20not%20hired%2C%20sources%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20that%20such%20media%20reports%20malign%20the%20fast-growing%20Indian%20manufacturing%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Labour%20and%20Employment%20on%20Wednesday%20has%20sought%20a%20detailed%20report%20from%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20labour%20department%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20married%20women%20not%20being%20allowed%20to%20work%20at%20the%20Foxconn%20India%20Apple%20iPhone%20Plant%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFoxconn%20had%20clarified%20that%2025%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20latest%20hires%20are%20married%20women.%20This%20would%20mean%20nearly%20one-third%20of%20the%20total%20women%20are%20married.%20This%20ratio%20compares%20favourably%20to%20any%20factory%20in%20this%20sector%20currently%20operating%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20sources%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Foxconn%20factory%20currently%20has%20about%2070%20per%20cent%20women%20and%2030%20per%20cent%20men%20and%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20plant%20is%20the%20largest%20factory%20for%20women%20employment%20in%20the%20country%20with%20the%20total%20employment%20having%20touched%2045%2C000%20workers%20during%20peak%20periods%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20also%20informed%20that%20the%20discussion%20around%20Hindu%20married%20women%20being%20discriminated%20against%20for%20wearing%20metals%20(ornaments%20and%20jewelry)%20is%20%26quot%3Bentirely%20slanted%26quot%3B%20and%20wearing%20metal%20in%20such%20factories%20is%20a%20safety%20issue%2C%20a%20fact%20well%20recognised%20by%20both%20the%20industry%20and%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20person%20wearing%20metals%20-%20man%20or%20woman%20-%20regardless%20of%20their%20status%20(single%20or%20married)%20and%20their%20religion%20(Hindu%2C%20Muslim%2C%20Christian%2C%20Sikh%20etc.)%20are%20required%20to%20remove%20metals%20while%20working%20in%20the%20factory%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said%20quoting%20the%20company's%20informal%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20safety%20reasons%2C%20no%20one%20wearing%20metal%20is%20allowed%20to%20work%20on%20the%20shop%20floor%20and%20this%20is%20a%20prevalent%20practice%20in%20several%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20the%20company%20has%20stated%20that%20the%20media%20report%20is%20based%20on%20anecdotal%20comments%20by%205-10%20people%20or%20potential%20job%20seekers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20comments%20likely%20came%20from%20candidates%20who%20did%20not%20get%20the%20job%20or%20no%20longer%20work%20at%20Foxconn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20immediate%20comments%20were%20received%20from%20Foxconn%20in%20response%20to%20an%20email%20query%20sent%20to%20the%20company%20on%20the%20matter.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719472020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fs6bgm1jg_foxconn-logo-ians_625x300_27_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A