22title%22%3A%22Samajwadi%20Party%20MP%20Wants%20Constitution%20To%20Replace%20'Sengol'%2C%20BJP%20Hits%20Back%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20'sengol'%20installed%20next%20to%20the%20Speaker's%20chair%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20latest%20flashpoint%20this%20Parliament%20session%20after%20Opposition%20MPs%20questioned%20its%20relevance%20in%20a%20democracy%20and%20the%20BJP%20accused%20them%20of%20disrespecting%20Indian%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20debate%20over%20'sengol'%2C%20a%20handcrafted%2C%20gold-plated%20sceptre%20about%205-feet%20long%2C%20has%20been%20triggered%20by%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MP%20RK%20Chaudhary's%20letter%20to%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla.%20The%20MP%20from%20Mohanlalganj%20has%20said%20the%20'sengol'%20must%20be%20replaced%20by%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20adoption%20of%20the%20Constitution%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20democracy%20in%20the%20country%2C%20and%20the%20Constitution%20is%20its%20symbol.%20The%20BJP%20government%20in%20its%20last%20term%20installed%20'sengol'%20next%20to%20the%20Speaker's%20chair.%20Sengol%20is%20a%20Tamil%20word%20that%20means%20sceptre.%20Rajdand%20also%20means%20the%20king's%20stick.%20We%20have%20become%20independent%20after%20the%20age%20of%20kings.%20Now%2C%20every%20man%20and%20woman%20who%20is%20an%20eligible%20voter%20chooses%20the%20government%20to%20run%20this%20country.%20So%20will%20the%20country%20run%20by%20Constitution%20or%20by%20a%20king's%20stick%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%C2%A0The%20former%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20minister%20demanded%20that%20the%20'sengol'%20be%20replaced%20by%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Constitution%20to%20%26quot%3Bsave%20democracy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20is%20the%20third-largest%20party%20in%20this%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20after%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20led%20it%20to%20a%20stellar%20show%20by%20winning%2037%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20his%20party%20MP's%20remark%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20'sengol'%20was%20installed%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20bowed%20to%20it.%20But%20he%20forgot%20to%20bow%20while%20taking%20oath%20this%20time.%20I%20think%20our%20MP%20wanted%20to%20remind%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20leader%20and%20MP%20B%20Manickam%20Tagore%20echoed%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MP%20on%20the%20'sengol'%20row.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20very%20clear%20that%20the%20'sengol'%20symbolises%20kingship%20and%20the%20kingdom-era%20is%20over.%20We%20should%20celebrate%20the%20people's%20democracy%20and%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chaudhary's%20demand%20was%20also%20backed%20by%20RJD%20MP%20and%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav's%20daughter%20Misa%20Bharti.%20%26quot%3BWhosoever%20has%20demanded%20this%2C%20I%20welcome%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition's%20'sengol'%20offensive%20also%20plays%20out%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20Constitution%20push%20to%20take%20on%20the%20third%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%20From%20the%20beginning%20of%20this%20session%2C%20the%20Constitution%20has%20been%20a%20common%20sight%20in%20the%20Opposition's%20gatherings.%20On%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20session%2C%20top%20INDIA%20leaders%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20among%20others%2C%20staged%20a%20demonstration%20on%20Parliament%20premises%20holding%20copies%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20The%20INDIA%20MPs%2C%20including%20Mr%20Gandhi%20and%20Mr%20Yadav%2C%20also%20held%20copies%20of%20the%20Constitution%20while%20taking%20the%20oath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20hit%20back%20at%20the%20Opposition%20over%20its%20'sengol'%20offensive.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20earlier%20attacked%20and%20abused%20Ramcharitmanas%2