perts-say%2Farticleshow%2F111301907.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fwill-prince-william-and-prince-harry-reconcile-what-experts-say%2Famp_articleshow%2F111301907.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fwill-prince-william-and-prince-harry-reconcile-what-experts-say%2Famp_articleshow%2F111301907.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Astronaut%20Sunita%20Williams'%20Return%20To%20Earth%20Delayed%20Again.%20What%20NASA%20Said%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian-origin%20astronaut%20Sunita%20Williams'%20scheduled%20return%20to%20Earth%20has%20been%20delayed%20once%20again%20after%20the%20spacecraft%20in%20which%20she%20travelled%20to%20space%2C%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%2C%20faced%20a%20series%20of%20technical%20glitches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20astronaut%2C%20who%20left%20Earth%20on%20June%205%20was%20set%20to%20return%20on%20June%2014%2C%20after%20a%20week%20in%20space.%20However%2C%20her%20return%20was%20delayed%20to%20June%2026.%20Now%2C%20no%20new%20date%20for%20her%20return%20has%20been%20disclosed%20by%20NASA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20had%20reported%20that%20the%20space%20agency%20had%20extended%20Ms%20Williams'%20stay%20on%20the%20space%20station%20after%20five%20helium%20leaks%20were%20detected%20on%20the%20Starliner%20spaceship%20and%20five%20of%20its%2028%20thrusters%20faced%20issues.%20At%20least%2014%20thrusters%20are%20needed%20for%20a%20safe%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20Ms%20Williams%20and%20her%20crewmate%20Butch%20Wilmore%20are%20both%20safe%20on%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20along%20with%20the%20seven%20other%20crew%20members.%20The%20ISS%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bmini%20city%20in%20space%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20size%20of%20a%20football%20field%20that%20astronauts%20from%20multiple%20space%20agencies%20use%20for%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20briefing%2C%20NASA%20said%20it%20is%20taking%20%26quot%3Bour%20time%20and%20following%20our%20standard%20mission%20management%20team%20process%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20spacecraft%20is%20clear%20for%20return%20in%20case%20of%20an%20emergency%20on%20the%20space%20station%20that%20requires%20the%20crew%20to%20come%20back%20to%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20agency%20said%20mission%20managers%20are%20evaluating%20future%20return%20opportunities%20following%20a%20planned%20spacewalk%20on%20July%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStarliner%20is%20performing%20well%20in%20orbit%20while%20docked%20to%20the%20space%20station.%20We%20are%20strategically%20using%20the%20extra%20time%20to%20clear%20a%20path%20for%20some%20critical%20station%20activities%20while%20completing%20readiness%20for%20Butch%20and%20Suni's%20return%20on%20Starliner%20and%20gaining%20valuable%20insight%20into%20the%20system%20upgrades%20we%20will%20want%20to%20make%20for%20post-certification%20missions%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20veteran%20astronaut%20returned%20to%20space%2C%20her%20flight%20was%20marred%20with%20several%20delays%20as%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%20spacecraft%20was%20repeatedly%20postponed%20by%20NASA.%20On%20June%207%2C%20the%20Indian-origin%20astronaut%20broke%20into%20a%20dance%20as%20she%20entered%20the%20space%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ms%20Williams%20has%20described%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfantastic%20spacecraft%26quot%3B%2C%20several%20whistleblowers%20have%20accused%20Boeing%20and%20NASA%20of%20neglect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20alleged%20that%20both%20Boeing%20and%20NASA%20managers%20knew%20of%20the%20technical%20faults%20with%20the%20spaceship%20but%20went%20ahead%20with%20the%20launch%20to%20avoid%20further%20delay.%20So%20far%2020%20whistleblowers%2C%20have%20accused%20NASA%20of%20ignoring%20their%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20aircraft%20maker%20Boeing%20has%20faced%20several%20allegations%20of%20technical%20failures%20as%20several%20of%20its%20aircrafts%20have%20suffered%20serious%20snags%20during%20flights%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719467100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F66j5ea08_sunita-williams_625x300_27_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fastronaut-sunita-williams-return-to-earth-delayed-again-what-nasa-said-5979727%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indian-origin%20astronaut%20Sunita%20Williams'%20scheduled%20return%20to%20Earth%20has%20been%20delayed%20once%20again%20after%20the%20spacecraft%20in%20which%20she%20travelled%20to%20space%2C%20the%20Boeing%20Starliner%2C%20faced%20a%20series%20of%20technical%20glitches.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fastronaut-sunita-williams-return-to-earth-delayed-again-what-nasa-said-5979727%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fastronaut-sunita-williams-return-to-earth-delayed-again-what-nasa-said-5979727%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fastronaut-sunita-williams-return-to-earth-delayed-again-what-nasa-said-5979727%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20vs.%20England%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20Livestream%3A%20How%20to%20Watch%20the%20T20%20Semifinal%20Online%20Free%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719467031000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FGettyImages-2159014739.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236050377%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20spot%20in%20the%20championship%20finals%20is%20up%20for%20grabs%20at%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup%20Thursday%2C%20as%20India%20and%20England%20face%20off%20in%20the%20second%20semifinal%20match%20of%20