less%20than%20what%20the%20agency%20had%20asked%20for.%20He%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20CBI%20inside%20the%20Rouse%20Avenue%20court.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20Rouse%20Avenue%20court%20had%20granted%20him%20bail%2C%20but%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20paused%20it%20and%20reserved%20its%20order.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20but%20got%20no%20relief.%20The%20high%20court%20thereafter%20denied%20him%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader's%20wife%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bwhole%20system%26quot%3B%20is%20trying%20to%20ensure%20he%20stays%20in%20jail.%20%26quot%3BArvind%20Kejriwal%20got%20bail%20on%20June%2020.%20Immediately%20ED%20got%20a%20stay.%20The%20very%20next%20day%20CBI%20made%20him%20an%20accused.%20And%20today%20he%20was%20arrested.%20The%20whole%20system%20is%20trying%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20man%20does%20not%20come%20out%20of%20jail.%20This%20is%20not%20law.%20This%20is%20dictatorship%2C%20this%20is%20emergency%2C%26quot%3B%20Sunita%20Kejriwal%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20'X'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%20for%20a%20three-day%20CBI%20custody%2C%20the%20Rouse%20Avenue%20court%20has%20said%20%26quot%3Binvestigation%20is%20the%20prerogative%20of%20the%20investigating%20agency%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20certain%20safeguards%20provided%20in%20the%20law%20and%20at%20this%20stage%2C%20on%20the%20material%20on%20record%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20said%20that%20the%20arrest%20is%20illegal.%20The%20agency%2C%20however%2C%20should%20not%20be%20overzealous%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20has%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20asked%20the%20central%20agency%20to%20produce%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20in%20court%20on%20Saturday.%20The%20court%20has%20said%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20may%20meet%20his%20wife%20for%20an%20hour%20daily.%20%26quot%3BLet%20the%20medically%20prescribed%20diet%2Fhome%20cooked%20food%20be%20provided%20to%20the%20accused%20during%20the%20police%20custody%20remand.%20Accused%20may%20also%20be%20provided%20with%20the%20prescribed%20medicines%20as%20well%20as%20glucometer%20during%20the%20remand.%20Accused%20be%20also%20allowed%20to%20take%20spectacles%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20has%20said%2C%20detailing%20the%20custody%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal's%20counsel%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20Vikram%20Chaudhari%2C%20had%20stressed%20that%20it%20was%20not%20necessary%20to%20arrest%20him%20at%20this%20stage%20and%20questioned%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20arrest.%20%26quot%3BThis%20court%20has%20to%20consider%2C%20at%20this%20stage%2C%20the%20merits%20of%20the%20case.%20The%20timing%20may%20be%20circumspect%20but%20it%20is%20not%20the%20clear%20criterion%20for%20declaring%20an%20arrest%20illegal%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20leader's%20counsel%20told%20that%20the%20CBI%20had%20questioned%20him%20in%20this%20connection%20for%20nine%20hours%20in%20April%20last%20year.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20then%20addressed%20the%20court%20directly%20and%20recounted%20what%20he%20had%20told%20CBI%20when%20he%20was%20asked%20why%20the%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy%20was%20framed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20told%20them%20(the%20CBI)%20there%20were%20three%20points.%20First%20-%20increase%20revenue.%20Second%20-%20reduce%20crowds%20to%20handle%20law%20and%20order.%20Third%20-%20opening%20of%20liquor%20shops%20in%20the%20right%20proportion%20(i.e.%2C%20equal%20distribution%20across%20the%20city).%20I%20had%20given%20instructions%20to%20Manish%20Sisodia%20(his%20former%20deputy%2C%20who%2C%20in%20February%20last%20year%2C%20was%20the%20first%20to%20be%20arrested%20in%20this%20case)%20to%20keep%20these%20three%20things%20in%20mind%20in%20the%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20poor%20citizen%20vs%20might%20of%20the%20State.%20This%20case%20is%20pending%20since%20August%202022.%20I%20was%20called%20as%20a%20witness...%20I%20appeared%20and%2C%20for%20nine%20hours%2C%20I%20assisted.%20Not%20a%20single%20notice%20(from%20the%20CBI)%20since%20then.%20How%20did%20they%20shift%20from%20a%20witness%20to%20an%20accused...%20it%20is%20a%20long%20distance%20to%20cover%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20counsel%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20termed%20the%20AAP%20leader's%20allegations%20%26quot%3Bunnecessary%26quot%3B.%20We%20could%20have%20done%20this%20before%2C%20or%20even%20during%2C%20the%20election.%20We%20did%20not...%20it%20(the%20interrogation)%20was%20done%20only%20after%20the%20court's%20permission.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20pointed%20out%20it%20was%20not%20bound%20to%20announce%20the%20start%20of%20an%20investigation.%20%26quot%3BSuppose%20there%20is%20an%20inquiry...%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20tell%20(Mr%20Kejriwal)...%20Who%20I%20have%20to%20tell%20is%20to%20the%20court%20-%20that%20I%20need%20custody.%20There%20is%20no%20mandate%20I%20have%20to%20tell%20the%20other%20side%20about%20my%20desire%20to%20investigate%2C%26quot%3B%20its%20counsel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719463320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F5piokgsg_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_27_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-delhi-liquor-policy-case-rouse-avenue-court-in-delhi-courts-custody-order-for-arvind-kejriwal-a-caveat-for-cbi-5979222%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20special%20CBI%20court%20that%20denied%20relief%20to%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case%20has%20said%20that%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20material%20on%20record%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20said%20at%20this%20stage%20that%20the%20arrest%20is%20illegal%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-delhi-liquor-policy-case-rouse-avenue-court-in-delhi-courts-custody-order-for-arvind-kejriwal-a-caveat-for-cbi-5979222%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%