02009%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Advani%20being%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20a%20parliamentary%20democracy%20was%20assumingly%20considered%20the%20BJP's%20Prime%20Ministerial%20candidate%20for%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20ending%20on%2016%20May%202009%2C%20according%20to%20the%20official%20website%20of%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2010%20December%202007%2C%20the%20Parliamentary%20Board%20of%20BJP%20formally%20announced%20Mr%20Advani%20as%20its%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20for%20the%20general%20elections%20due%20in%202009.%20But%20when%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20won%20the%202009%20general%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Advani%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20to%20become%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%2015th%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719461820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fblv3me48_lk-advani_625x300_03_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flk-advani-admitted-to-aiims-delhi-5978269%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Senior%20and%20veteran%20leader%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani%2C%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(AIIMS)%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flk-advani-admitted-to-aiims-delhi-5978269%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flk-advani-admitted-to-aiims-delhi-5978269%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flk-advani-admitted-to-aiims-delhi-5978269%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nepal%20Rains%3A%20Landslides%2C%20floods%2C%20and%20lightning%20kill%2014%22%2C%22content%22%3A