into%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%2C%20Indian-American%20radiologist%20Dharmesh%20Patel%20has%20avoided%20a%20jail%20term%20and%20will%20be%20treated%20for%20mental%20illness%20after%20his%20doctors%20told%20the%20court%20he%20suffered%20a%20%26quot%3Bpsychotic%20breakdown%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202023%2C%20Mr%20Patel%20drove%20his%20Tesla%2C%20carrying%20his%20wife%20Neha%20and%20two%20children%20aged%207%20and%204%2C%20off%20a%20cliff%20into%20a%20250-foot%20gorge.%20The%20family%20escaped%20with%20minor%20injuries%20even%20though%20the%20car%20was%20severely%20damaged.%20His%20wife%20told%20rescuers%20he%20drove%20the%20car%20off%20the%20cliff%20intentionally%20and%20was%20mentally%20disturbed%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EWhy%20did%20he%20drive%20his%20car%20off%20a%20cliff%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Mr%20Patel's%20lawyers%20told%20the%20court%20that%20his%20actions%20were%20solely%20influenced%20by%20his%20mental%20state%20as%20he%20was%20suffering%20from%20paranoia%20and%20delusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20who%20assessed%20the%20radiologist%20said%20his%20mental%20health%20had%20deteriorated%20weeks%20before%20the%20horrific%20crash.%20He%20had%20been%20hearing%20footsteps%20and%20was%20convinced%20he%20was%20being%20followed%20by%20someone%2C%20the%20doctors%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20believed%20his%20children%20were%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20kidnapped%20and%20sexually%20assaulted%20or%20trafficked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patel%2C%20who%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%20to%20three%20charges%20of%20attempted%20murder%2C%20has%20now%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20schizoaffective%20disorder%20and%20major%20depressive%20disorder.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20paranoid%20and%20kind%20of%20delusional%20thinking%20that%20he%20acted%20on%20at%20the%20time%20to%20protect%20his%20family%20from%20a%20worse%20fate%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20psychologist%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3EWhat%20happens%20next%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20US%20judge%20decided%20that%20the%20radiologist%20was%20eligible%20for%20a%20'mental%20health%20diversion'%2C%20a%20provision%20in%20the%20law%20that%20allows%20an%20accused%20with%20mental%20illness%20to%20get%20mental%20health%20treatment%20instead%20of%20serving%20jail%20time%20if%20the%20illness%20played%20a%20huge%20role%20in%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuperior%20Court%20Judge%20Susan%20M.%20Jakubowski%20determined%20that%20Mr%20Patel%20was%20eligible%20for%20the%20diversion%20based%20on%20his%20doctors'%20diagnosis%20and%20ordered%20he%20be%20released%20to%20his%20parents%20in%20California.%20He%20will%20be%20monitored%20with%20GPS%20and%20report%20to%20the%20court%20once%20a%20week.%20He%20is%20also%20not%20allowed%20to%20travel%20outside%20his%20country%20and%20must%20surrender%20his%20driving%20license%20and%20passport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20will%20now%20be%20placed%20on%20a%20two-year%20treatment%20plan%20and%20charges%20against%20him%20would%20be%20dropped%20if%20he%20doesn't%20commit%20any%20crimes%20during%20the%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719460260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fju68blug_dharmesh-patel_625x300_27_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fdharmesh-patel-why-indian-american-doctor-drove-car-with-wife-2-children-off-us-cliff-5979113%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20year%20after%20he%20drove%20his%20wife%20and%20two%20children%20off%20a%20cliff%20in%20California%20into%20the%20Pacific%20Ocean%2C%20Indian-American%20radiologist%20Dharmesh%20Patel%20has%20avoided%20a%20jail%20term%20and%20will%20be%20treated%20for%20mental%20illness.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fdharmesh-patel-why-indian-american-doctor-drove-car-with-wife-2-children-off-us-cliff-5979113%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.