.%20The%20GWOT%20had%20them%20knocking%20down%20doors%2C%20and%20in%202024%2C%20shotguns%20found%20a%20new%20niche%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20cheap%2C%20mass-produced%2C%20civilian%2C%20and%20even%20toy-grade%20drones%20has%20changed%20the%20battlefield.%20In%20many%20ways%2C%20drones%20are%20the%20new%20Improvised%20Explosive%20Devices.%20They%20are%20a%20new%2C%20extremely%20dangerous%20threat%20that%20doesn't%20comply%20with%20the%20tactics%20we'd%20been%20taught%20for%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%20The%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20has%20cemented%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sandboxx.us%2Fnews%2Fsmashing-drones-with-a-standard-rifle-may-be-the-best-way-to-counter-them%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecommercial%20drones%20as%20potent%20weapons%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20like%20aircraft%20in%20World%20War%20I%2C%20commercial%20drones%20started%20life%20as%20reconnaissance%20assets%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20long%20until%20they%20were%20weaponized.%20Given%20the%20size%20and%20price%20of%20commercial%20drones%2C%20they%20are%20remarkably%20efficient%20and%20extremely%20deadly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20high-tech%20counter-drone%20measures%20have%20been%20employed%2C%20and%20more%20are%20being%20developed.%20While%20these%20tools%20are%20few%20and%20unrefined%2C%20the%20humble%20shotgun%20has%20once%20more%20emerged%20as%20a%20potential%20anti-commercial%20drone%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d006043-80ef-4ef0-b733-c23097bff2b3%5C%22%3EThe%20shotgun%20as%20a%20drone%20killer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224928%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Girls%20examine%20a%20pump-action%20shotgun%20during%20shooting%20training%20for%20civilians%20outside%20the%20Ukrainian%20city%20of%20Kharkiv.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667c8f29d1c84a0eaca82351%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGirls%20