20skills%20through%20workshops%2C%20courses%2C%20talks%2C%20and%20articles.%20They%20focus%20on%20providing%20insights%20into%20brain%20and%20child%20development%2C%20alongside%20offering%20strategies%20for%20fostering%20positive%20communication%20and%20effective%20discipline.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWorking%20with%20parents%20across%20diverse%20groups%20in%20multiple%20languages%20in%20schools%20(both%20private%20and%20government)%2C%20corporates%2C%20and%20at%20an%20individual%20level%2C%20Parenting%20Matters%20is%20dedicated%20to%20the%20conviction%20that%20by%20supporting%20families%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20transformation%20towards%20a%20healthier%20and%20more%20caring%20community%2C%20one%20family%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719408628000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D354393%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parenting%20Matters%20has%20been%20working%20with%20parents%20for%20over%2020%20years%20to%20help%20them%20figure%20out%20effective%20and%20sensitive%20ways%20to%20raise%20their%20children.%20Their%20main%20focus%20is%20to%20undo%20the%20past%20where%20anger%2C%20intolerance%2C%20and%20disrespect%20governed%20parent-children%20relationships.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Assam%2C%20Solar%20Energy%20Helps%20Doctors%20%26amp%3B%20Medicines%20Reach%20Island%20Dwellers%20on%20Boats%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20June%2C%20check%20out%20our%20%23ApnaGharSolar%20series%2C%20an%20exclusive%20deep%20dive%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20in%20collaboration%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.solarsquare.in%2F%3Futm_source%3Dsocialmedia%26utm_medium%3Dad%26utm_campaign%3DTheBetterIndia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESolarSquare%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20solar%20power%20boom.%20Stay%20tuned%20for%20more%20interesting%20stories%2C%20data%20and%20information!%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Saddam%20Hussain%20from%20Silchar%20left%20his%20home%20around%207%20am%20for%20his%20camp%20duty%20in%20Sadhu%20Sapori%20village%20of%20Majuli%20district%20%E2%80%93%20a%20large%20river%20island%20formed%20by%20the%20majestic%20Brahmaputra%20river%20and%20its%20tributaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20four%20hours%20of%20the%20boat%20ride%2C%20Dr%20Saddam%20reached%20the%20village%20along%20with%20his%20team%20of%20healthcare%20workers.%20It%20was%20not%20the%20regular%20OPD%20clinic%20of%20a%20city%20hospital.%20Here%2C%20the%20camp%20was%20set-up%20by%20the%20river%20bank.%20The%20community%20is%20always%20delighted%20to%20see%20the%20healthcare%20workers%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20morning%2C%20I%20have%20seen%20at%20least%2050%20patients%20who%20complained%20of%20abdominal%20pain%2C%20urinary%20tract%20infections%2C%20hypertension%2C%20joint%20pains%2C%20skin%20related%20diseases%3B%20and%20those%20who%20required%20antenatal%20care%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Saddam%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20healthcare%20gap%20in%20the%20region%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20flooding%20of%20the%20Brahmaputra%20river%20affects%20a%20large%20population%20residing%20in%20the%20islands.%20Whenever%20it%20rains%20heavily%20in%20Arunachal%2C%20the%20river%20water%20rises.%20There%20are%20no%20sub-centres%20in%20the%20islands.%20We%20are%20the%20only%20healthcare%20workers%20for%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-2-1719399558.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Riturekha