d%20power%20to%20make%20a%20change.%20People-centricity%20was%20a%20major%20driving%20force.%20I%20felt%20administration%20was%20a%20way%20to%20lead%20a%20purpose-driven%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20he%20quit%20the%20job%20and%20started%20preparing%20for%20UPSC.%20With%2010%20months%20of%20preparation%2C%20Ashish%20managed%20to%20clear%20prelims%20in%20his%20very%20first%20attempt.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20focussed%20on%20prelims%20but%20I%20did%20not%20prepare%20for%20Mains%20at%20all.%20I%20was%20in%20a%20celebratory%20mood.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20realised%20I%20needed%20to%20prepare%20for%20Mains%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20wasted%20a%20month%20and%20had%20just%20two%20months%20left%20for%20preparation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20expected%2C%20Ashish%20failed%20the%20Mains%20in%202018.%20%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20that%20my%20preparation%20was%20not%20sufficient%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20motivated%20to%20attempt%20again%20but%20sadly%2C%20he%20failed%20the%20prelims%20in%20the%20second%20attempt%20in%202020.%20In%20his%20third%20attempt%20in%202021%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20clear%20the%20prelims%20but%20missed%20the%20Mains%20cut%20off%20by%2020%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-2-1718972776.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ashish%20graduated%20from%20IIT%20Kharagpur%20and%20later%20on%20quit%20a%20well-paying%20job%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20civil%20service.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-2-1718972776.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-2-1718972776-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%