to%20clear%20UPSC%20CSE%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Be%20Consistent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20the%20fifth%20attempt%2C%20I%20knew%20what%20I%20needed%20to%20study%2C%20but%20I%20lacked%20consistency.%20If%20you%20have%20decided%20to%20become%20a%20civil%20servant%2C%20you%20must%20work%20hard%20consistently.%20So%2C%20if%20you%20study%20for%20four%20days%20and%20then%20rest%20for%20the%20next%20four%20days%2C%20then%20you%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20achieve%20success.%20It%E2%80%99s%20better%20to%20study%20all%20eight%20days%20even%20though%20for%20fewer%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20How%20to%20read%20the%20newspaper%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshish%20says%20his%20day%20started%20by%20reading%20the%20newspaper%20%E2%80%94%20either%20The%20Hindu%20or%20The%20Indian%20Express.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20read%20the%20newspaper%20for%20about%20an%20hour.%20The%20strategy%20to%20read%20the%20newspaper%20should%20be%20different%20for%20aspirants.%20Usually%2C%20people%20look%20for%20%3Cem%3Emasala%20%3C%2Fem%3Enews%20but%20as%20an%20aspirant%2C%20I%20looked%20for%20topics%20related%20to%20constitution%2C%20environment%2C%20or%20economy.%20A%20few%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337399%2Fbihar-ias-officer-anshuman-raj-cracked-upsc-cse-without-coaching-success-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoaching%20centres%20%3C%2Fa%3Elike%20Vajiram%20also%20publish%20important%20news%20items%20on%20their%20social%20media%20pages%2C%20mark%20those%20in%20the%20newspaper%20and%20read%20about%20them%20in%20detail%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReading%20the%20newspaper%20daily%20widens%20your%20thought%20process.%20%E2%80%9CSuppose%20there%20is%20an%20editorial%20on%20international%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20China%2C%20journalists%20take%20information%20from%20history%20and%20other%20sources%20to%20com