20to%20minimise%20source%20material.%20%E2%80%9CRely%20on%20one%20or%20two%20sources%20that%20help%20you%20complete%20the%20syllabus%20for%20a%20subject.%20Do%20not%20get%20distracted%20by%20multiple%20sources.%20Initially%2C%20I%20was%20also%20in%20the%20trap%20of%20purchasing%20multiple%20books%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20better%20to%20fix%20your%20sources%20and%20study%20from%20the%20same%20source%20again%20and%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20advises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20source%20material%2C%20Ashish%20informs%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20studied%20NCERTs%20from%20Standard%206%20to%2012%20for%20almost%20all%20subjects%20to%20develop%20foundational%20knowledge.%20I%20referred%20to%20standard%20books%20like%20Laxmikant%20for%20Polity%20and%20Bipin%20Chandra%20for%20Modern%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Use%20colourful%20highlighters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20vast%20syllabus%2C%20Ashish%20says%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20tendency%20to%20forget%20topics.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20very%20important%20to%20revise.%20I%20used%20to%20underline%20or%20make%20circles%20on%20important%20points.%20I%20would%20also%20use%20different%20colours%20of%20highlighters%20or%20pens%20to%20mark%20the%20important%20topics.%20Make%20short%20notes%20for%20points%20that%20you%20keep%20forgetting%20even%20after%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351050%2Fupsc-cse-how-to-make-notes-ips-officer-rishabh-bhola-shares-tips-tricks-techniques%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiple%20revisions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20IAS%20Ashish%20Kumar%20Singhal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718974639000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIAS-Ashish-1-1718972736.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D353815%22%2C